profile:
Frogbox rents reusable, industrial strength, stack-able moving boxes. We will drop off the boxes and pick them up after your move and save you and the environment the impact of using cardboard. The environmental ramification of using cardboard is significant as it makes up an estimated 18-20% of landfill material. If you are moving between cities where there are Frogbox locations you can have the Frogboxes dropped off in one city and picked up in another. Make your move easier by using Frogbox eco-friendly reusable moving boxes and other moving supplies. We have worked with all the Movers in the cities we service and can refer credible movers (and tell you who to avoid :)).  
FROGBOX was a successful contender on The Dragon's Den.

profile:
Aleks moving started in 2007 with family at the core, we are family owned and operated and we put that care we have for our own family into the care we show for our clients and their belongings. Moving can be stressful so we ensure we take the time to do a walkthrough with you, to carefully pack (if needed)  and load/unload your belongings safely and carefully.

 During these times we also work to ensure all of our staff are equipped with the proper safety gear and that our moving equipment and trucks are cleaned and sanitized prior to your move, we also offer FLAT RATE FEE and offer 24/7 care and service. We offer the best rates in Ontario. CALL US TODAY FOR A FREE ESTIMATE


• All staff are equipped and trained with safety gear, such as masks, gloves, clothing + hand sanitizer
• Aleks Moving has implemented strict and extensive cleaning and sanitizing practices for all our moving equipment like blankets and straps, and the interior and exterior of our trucks
• We are constantly monitoring each staff for symptoms and encouraging them to stay home if they are not feeling well
• One person social distancing walk through of your home prior to your move to ensure everything is clear and understood. 

Please stay safe , wash yours hands often and practice social distancing. 

Free estimates at your convenience, including coming out to your home to view what you have to move so we have a better understanding so that on the day of the move there are no surprises for you or the movers. packing and unpacking if required, protection of all furniture, dismantling and reassembling, short and long-term storage, inventory service, and many other services.

profile:
Quality service at an affordable price.

We're VR MOVING, a local, family-owned and operated professional moving service in Mississauga. Our local movers can handle moves of any size, including apartments, condos, single-family homes, retirement communities, dorms and more. VR MOVING is also specialized in moving any size of pianos, safes. When you move with us, you know your things will be safe. Before we move anything, our professional movers will protect your furniture with our heavy duty storage blankets. We also carry shrink wrap if your items need an extra layer of protection. To prevent any damage to large furniture items, we use shoulder harness straps and padded dollies. We also make sure we protect all your hardwood and tile floors when we get to your home. 
When you choose VR Moving, you know you’ll always get:
Upfront rates, with no hidden fees
On-time service
Friendly, uniformed movers
Fully licensed, insured, & honest service
When you arrange for a move with us, we’ll take care of everything. From showing up on time to keeping your costs as low as possible, you can feel confident that your project is in good hands. 
With over five  years of experience, in 2021 we started VR MOVING INC. While moving can be very stressful and can’t be cheap, the last thing people need is the unfair & over priced cost of a “professional” moving services. We believe there is a way to provide valuable, honest and professional moving services at an affordable prices. We're very excited to serve our community and we are committed to provide honest services.

profile:
When moving your home from Point A to Point B, you need trustworthy experts who can handle everything from A to Z - with TLC. 
Swan Moving & Storage specializes in full household moves of your furniture across the province, town or street. It's a company that emphasizes quality service. 
Owner Mike Swan began his first moving venture in 1972 while taking English at the University of Guelph. Business was booming, so he kept it going after graduation. 
Today, Swan can move up to six complete households per day! 
Their specialized service includes office, commercial, executive transfers, antiques and pianos. In fact, they move up to 350 pianos per year.

***
All-Ways Moving & Storage is your best choice for an excellent quality, customer oriented moving company in Nova Scotia, Windsor, Halifax and the Annapolis Valley. All-ways Moving & Storage head office is located in Newport, Nova Scotia. We serve customers from all across Canada including but not limited to Windsor, Mount Uniacke, Wolfville, Hantsport, Berwick, Annapolis, Halifax, Dartmouth, and westward on to Toronto, Calgary, Vancouver and many other Canadian cities. 800 MILES IS AS FAR AS WE SERVICE.
***
Be assured your move is done right - Use All-Ways Moving & Storage and see & feel the difference.

profile:
Defined by hard work and efficiency, Macho Movers Moving Company is a local moving company based out of Guelph, Ontario. Created by head Macho, Brad Veldman,  our goal is to provide Southwestern Ontario with an affordable moving solution that encompasses the need for safety and efficiency. 
Using all of the best technology to ensure your products are secured and taken good care of, our Moving Experts will move you out of your old space and into your new one in remarkable time.
We provide more than just the muscle to get you out of your old space and into your new. Packing your personal belongings is just one extra we offer that some of the other guys don't. Preparation for a move can be truly grueling, but Macho Movers are prepared to take the headache away.
Macho Movers also specializes in junk removal, as we have some of the best resources to get rid of that old rubbish to the landfill, or more environmentally viable options. Last but not least, there isn't any request we won't entertain. Do you have an excruciating job, fit for a bunch of Macho Movers? Give us a call and we will try our very best to make your wishes come true. Don't believe us? Just check out our testimonials on  our website!
